prompt_template:
Write a cold email.

Inputs:
- Sender: {{sender}}
- Recipient role: {{recipient_role}}
- Product/service: {{offer}}
- Value proposition: {{value_prop}}
- Call to action: {{cta}}

Constraints:
- 120-170 words
- No hype, no exclamation marks
- Clear subject line

Output format:
Subject: ...

Body:
...
